      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<p>Ready to get the most value from your Liferay Support? Here are the next steps for getting started:</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><b>Review</b> our <a href=\"/w/service-levels\">Service Levels</a> so you know exactly what to expect.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><b>Dig into</b> the details of our <a href=\"/v/25988285\">Support Coverage</a> to understand what we cover, and when.</p>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>\n\t<p><b>Discover</b> the <a href=\"/v/26066836\">best practices for reporting issues</a> to us, so you can get the fastest resolution possible.</p>\n\t</li>\n</ul>"
      },
